item.title: Afterhours - Episode: Move On Up
item.description: International duo, Gemini Rising, provide a fine array of danceable tracks every other Friday on We Take No Requests Radio. Download this one hour classic episode of Afterhours, featuring a superb mix of new wave, rock, electronic and dance classics. This 1 hour mix includes new music from DIGITALISM, ROISIN MURPHY, CHROMEO, SIMIAN MOBILE DISCO, DURAN DURAN, BUMBLEBEEZ, A-TRAK, and THE FLYING LIZARDS plus JUSTICE, CANSEI DE SER SEXY, CALVIN HARRIS, JAY Z, AME, GEMENI RISING, MARK RONSON, and more.
item.itunes:author: wtnrradio@gmail.com - Gemini Rising
